{"tid":1548157,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"兔子不親人的誤會而被棄養 !","createTime":"2019-09-07T02:38:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T05:41:17.000Z","uid":197098,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"05c24e7db22ce0e926baad6c17cb6fd23046e41a","tid":1548157,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:38:39.000Z","msg":"有些人會問: 為什麼我在東, 牠會面向著西?<br />\n<br />\n其實兔子<ins><em>側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西</em></ins>。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面睇唔到)&nbsp;<ins><em>你在他後面也會看到你</em></ins>。兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。所以佢地唔係無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱。另外也有遠視。<br />\n<br />\n兔子🐰是親人的群體性動物，但身體語言與其他動物不同，要做些研究才理解。(推介最底的3個網站)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">親人的動物：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMaovq8Vz1LM&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAU%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=a7e07c3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpyL0yEs-ka8&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAU%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=f86c89b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">兔子的行為解釋網站：</span><br />\n<br />\n香港兔協:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2Fknowledge8_ch.php&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAU%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=72bb911a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php</a><br />\n<br />\n美國兔協 House Rabbit Society (教育網站):&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAU%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=7f15156e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a><br />\n<br />\n詳盡身體語言解釋(喜怒哀樂):&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAU%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=a746abd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a>"},{"pid":"9e68954547652612cf60e58d6ff6888e296eb20b","tid":1548157,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:39:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e495a62871b2b38173456241f18f1acc61849ac7","tid":1548157,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:46:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XNJmeXb4Y0A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXNJmeXb4Y0A&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAU%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=431bc770\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XNJmeXb4Y0A</a>"},{"pid":"d123ce8574b17cccd76659f2657c68ff4790f64f","tid":1548157,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:54:16.000Z","msg":"兔子同屋企小朋友玩耍, 是人類的朋友 !!<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AyUYeLrXqug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAyUYeLrXqug&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAU%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=fa8da419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AyUYeLrXqug</a>"},{"pid":"743fd691334b33db84111160dc50b82d6faedc60","tid":1548157,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:00:15.000Z","msg":"兔子是一種心境平靜的動物，很多人覺得牠們咀嚼食物的聲音很治癒。如果你家的兔子有攻擊性，這不是牠的本性，而是後天環境和飼養方式影響的。兔子亦被作為情緒和心靈支持動物(emotional support animal)，即是主人有醫生的證明，帶着小動物作伴，心靈才得到慰藉。<br />\n<br />\n以下video可看到兔子拚命地拯救一隻被困住的貓! 真感人！☺<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FydwwZtQyuiU&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAU%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=94e3f72f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU</a>"},{"pid":"653be6c510598b134baaeefd2cd0afa3d641842f","tid":1548157,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:02:41.000Z","msg":"你都幾撚煩 兔係用來食架"},{"pid":"35bffdb7dd19e750c54139554b876c6c354f7fa5","tid":1548157,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:42:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>兔子的睡窩被貓霸佔了 !</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n兔子是被捕獵的動物(prey animal)，在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predator)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2HMWjTXFwuY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2HMWjTXFwuY&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAU%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=f64e680a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2HMWjTXFwuY</a>"},{"pid":"31deb98212eb9cf59bf4d1699b8634d5d1b40e7f","tid":1548157,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:06:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>寵物兔是應該要被絕育</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):</span><br />\n<br />\n1.&nbsp;兔子是被捕獵動物(Prey animal), 是大自然內每個捕獵者(Predator)的目標, 狗吠聲、消防車叫聲、小孩尖叫、雷暴等也會嚇驚兔子, 所以不建議帶出外散步。兔子是全世界其中一個最多被棄養的動物(在美國排第3最多被棄養), 很多人將牠放生, 這樣會令兔子十分恐慌, 而且沒有覓食能力(寵物兔和野兔是不同), 有些人送給兔協, 但容納不到那麼龐大的數目。<br />\n<br />\n2.&nbsp;絕育後會大大減少因荷爾蒙控制而霸地盤，不會隨地去廁所 (兔子是不需要訓練去廁所，只要廁所內有紙棉和乾草和夠大便可以, 建議用貓廁所)<br />\n<br />\n3.&nbsp;荷爾蒙減少令攻擊性減少，更加溫馴和親人，也會活得更開心。如果想將2隻兔合養(做夫妻/好朋友)要先絕育才容易建立關係, 否則有機會打架！<br />\n<br />\n4.&nbsp;兔子是很容易患上生殖器病動物，所以絕育會令到更健康和長壽！<br />\n<br />\n5.&nbsp;減少過量繁殖(和棄養後所面對的困境)，繁殖得快和多。"},{"pid":"3d6a79a2692079a476b9b638d93e0c5c6536d670","tid":1548157,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:54:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>兔子開心到極!</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n跳兔子舞(Binky)是兔子最開心的狀態。這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活。兔子也會舒適地躺在地上，伸展手腳，還會打翻騰。室內飼養會比室外養長命，因為沒有天氣和敵人威脅，感到安全、平靜和舒適。狗吠聲、雷暴、消防車叫聲等也會嚇驚兔子。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom(撫摸/親吻)牠們，令牠們冷靜下來知道是沒事的。我家的兔子一聽到吸塵機聲音就嚇驚，所以每次我工人吸塵的時候，我會一直撫摸他們，幾次後他們已習慣了 !<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpqOeRBSpaCs&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAU%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=cf7a4b81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE90ikFGQTqs&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAU%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=32f46501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs</a>"},{"pid":"1d778861dcc050cee3dde2a2ebe2035f4b137917","tid":1548157,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:27:21.000Z","msg":"兔子發夢同主人玩：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s-7b9X5x_Ro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs-7b9X5x_Ro&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAU%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=a3830ac0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s-7b9X5x_Ro</a>"},{"pid":"5036f0274f6a74378cfbcd750d2938ff8f9edc7f","tid":1548157,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:10:28.000Z","msg":"兔子發夢飲水:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkoTWmdwLlp8&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAU%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=b21a949f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8</a>"},{"pid":"60cef2c0d80e91846d7150f65eaabc9057d174b9","tid":1548157,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:03:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">兔子不滿吃飯時被拍攝，上前搞灣2部攝錄機</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lE5Qexr-jos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlE5Qexr-jos&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAU%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=2231a5dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lE5Qexr-jos</a>"},{"pid":"7c2e506fc31763ddc08e04bdc179b12848676c12","tid":1548157,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}